Sorry for the lack of description, I have like 1 min to write this 
post. (My comp's been crashing and I'm using a friend's)


::Scyther/Killfest/Firearm/Incarcinator/Greven/Demise/Grimmler/Fliq::

Scyther yells in pain as all of the shots hit him, his cloak failing 
and making him visible again. He flies at Riona, slashing his scythe 
at her.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Two shots, along with Firearm's charge, zoom by Killfest as he spins 
out of the way, flying at Firearm again.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm aims his cannon at Killfest, firing two charges.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator laughs, beginning to crush Prowl with his superior grip.

"It was a mistake ramming me, Maximal," he says, trying to squeeze 
hard enough for Prowl's torso to give in, but not being able to due 
to Prowl's superior armor. Prowl smashes his palm into Incarcinator's 
stomach, trying to get him away.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Greven dodges the shots fired at him, firing his gun to destroy 
several missiles. He aims at Sky Lynx, firing two missiles at the bot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Demise is hit by the shots fired at him, sending him flying backwards.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Grimmler's shuttle evades most of the shots, firing its cannons back 
at the Predacon shuttles.
